Utterance.UttText: In Bed 5, we have Yvonne Matthews, 26 yrs old, under Dr Gordon came in with head injury.
She sustained the injury while she was playing basketball.
The team are planning to have a surgery for her but is still waiting for the surgeons to review her CT results.
She complain of headache today and endone given with good effect.
She is self caring and ambulant.
She's got her mother in attendance.
She is very anxious and very demanding. otherwise she is stable
